009package imagingbook.sampleimages;
010
011import imagingbook.core.resource.ImageResource;
012
013/**
014 * Enumeration defining a set of {@link ImageResource} objects associated
015 * with MSER test images.
016 * @see ImageResource
017 * @see GeneralTestImage
018 */
019public enum MserTestImage implements ImageResource {
020        AllBlack("all-black.png"),
021        AllWhite("all-white.png"),  
022        Blob1("blob1.png"),
023        Blob2("blob2.png"),
024        Blob3("blob3.png"),          
025        BlobLevelTestNoise("blob-level-test-noise.png"),
026        BlobsInWhite("blobs-in-white.png"),  
027        BoatsTinyB("boats-tiny-b.png"),   
028        BoatsTinyW("boats-tiny-w.png"),
029        BlobLevelTest("blob-level-test.png"),  
030        BlobOriented("blob-oriented.png"),          
031        BoatsTiny("boats-tiny.png"),      
032        BoatsTinyBW("boats-tiny-bw.png"),  
033        BoatsTinyW2("boats-tiny-w2.png");
034        
035        private final String filename;
036        
037        MserTestImage(String filename) {
038                this.filename = filename;
039        }
040        
041        @Override
042        public String getFileName() {
043                return filename;
044        }
045}
